# 🤖 AI Resume Screening System

An AI-powered Applicant Tracking System (ATS) built with **Streamlit**, **Sentence Transformers**, and **Python**. The application analyzes, ranks, and compares candidate resumes against a job description using semantic similarity, skill matching, and resume analysis. It also generates professional PDF reports for recruiters.

---

## Features

- Upload Job Description (PDF)
- Upload Multiple Candidate Resumes (PDF)
- Automatic Resume Parsing
- Semantic Similarity Matching
- ATS Score Calculation
- Skill Match Analysis
- Missing Skills Identification
- Candidate Ranking Dashboard
- Candidate Search and Filters
- Candidate Comparison
- AI Candidate Summary
- Hiring Recommendation
- Professional PDF Report Generation
- Interactive Analytics Dashboard
- CSV Export
- Clean and Modular Streamlit Interface

